-- Honda August U.S. auto sales fall 7.3 percent
-- 
-- Wed Sep 3, 2008 2:12pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/09/03/us-usa-autosales-honda-idUSWNAB928520080903

 

 DETROIT  (Reuters) - Honda Motor Co Ltd said on Wednesday that U.S. auto sales fell 7.3 percent to 146,855 units in August. 

 Honda brand car sales fell 4.9 percent to 78,674 vehicles in August, while Honda brand light truck sales fell 10.3 percent to 53,092 vehicles. Sales in its luxury Acura division fell 8.2 percent to 15,089 vehicles. (Reporting by  David Bailey )